Invocation Name: dungeons deloy
des: Skill created by Ian Maclean, Brett Barker, and George Black for their applied IT class. Create your own adventure game based around your senior year at Greenville University. The goal is to make it to graduation by obtaining 20 points in the three categories (social, grades, and purity).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
